GME Password Reset Instructions


Connect to the corporate network

Use SAW and VPN
Open Pulse Secure and connect to GFS‑VPN

Go to the OneIdentity portal

https://oneidentity.core.windows.net


Sign in

Use your @gme.gbl certificate (smart card / YubiKey)


Reset the password

Select Create/Modify
Domain: gme
Enter your alias
Click Reset Password



Retrieve and save the password

Click View Password
Save it securely (you cannot reset again for 24 hours)
